@startuml
actor User
participant UI
participant API
participant ApplianceService
participant Database
participant Events

User -> UI: Add Appliance
UI -> API: POST /api/appliances
API -> ApplianceService: RegisterAppliance(dto)
ApplianceService -> Database: Insert
ApplianceService -> Events: Publish(ApplianceRegistered)
API --> UI: 201 Created
UI --> User: Show Success
@enduml
